To compile the test suite run make:

   make test

To compile the tests with robust debugging notes, you can use the debug flag:

   make DF=DEBUG test

To run the entire test suite:

   ./test

To run a single test from the test suite:

   ./test [QUEUE, LOCKING, LOCKFREEC, AWESOME]

To run an experiment as described in the assignment

   make
   ./project4 -e experiment number



